  "description": {
    "zh": "你好。我想你已经了解最近的情况了，既然你找到了Jaeger带给我的血样。我分析了它们，但还不够。\n\n要开始工作，我需要病毒本身的样本。这极其危险，任务中请使用所有防护措施！\n\n一旦找到就立刻来见我。这是为了最小化病毒暴露在开放环境中的时间。",
    "en": "Greetings. I figure you're already aware of the recent situation, granted you've found the blood samples Jaeger brought me. I've analyzed them, but it's not sufficient.\n\nIn order to get started, I need a sample of the virus itself. This is extremely dangerous, so use every precaution during the mission!\n\nCome and see me as soon as you find it. This is to minimize the time the virus is out in the open."
  },
